item.title: TFLearn
item.author: LiuDongdong
item.description: TFlearn is a modular and transparent deep learning library built on top of Tensorflow. It was designed to provide a higher-level API to TensorFlow in order to facilitate and speed-up experimentations, while remaining fully transparent and compatible with it. 1. layers File Layers core input_data, fully_connected, dropout, custom_layer, reshape, flatten, activation, single_unit, highway, one_hot_encoding, time_distributed conv conv_2d, conv_2d_transpose, max_pool_2d, avg_pool_2d, upsample_2d, conv_1d, max_pool_1d, avg_pool_1d, residual_block, residual_bottleneck, conv_3d, max_pool_3d, avg_pool_3d, highway_conv_1d,
